### Pure CSS Parallax Implementation
**CRITICAL:** Parallax is achieved with pure CSS, not JavaScript.

```css
/* Parallax using background-attachment: fixed */
.parallax-bg {
  background-attachment: fixed;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
}

/* Respects reduced motion preferences */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  .parallax-bg {
    background-attachment: fixed;
  }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .parallax-bg {
    background-attachment: scroll;
  }
}
```

**Benefits:**
- Better performance (no JavaScript calculations)
- Respects accessibility preferences automatically
- Simpler codebase
- Works even if JavaScript fails

